<title>USA: Classic Restaurants says gets $750,000.</title>
<headline>Classic Restaurants says gets $750,000.</headline>
<dateline>NORCROSS, Ga. 1997-05-23</dateline>
<text>
<p>Classic Restaurants International Inc said Friday it received a commitment for $750,000 in financing contingent on the closing of its proposed merger with the privately held Main Event Inc.</p>
<p>The company said it would release further details &quot;shortly.&quot;</p>
<p>The previously announced deal involves an exchange of Main Event's restaurant and nightclub operations for Classic Restaurant's shares.</p>
<p>Main event is a Dallas-based restaurant and entertainment management company.</p>
